到通知稱現場有人聚集或有警員受襲。辯方播放現場閉路電視片段，顯示警方到達前兩分鐘，被告與一名女士經過，當時現場並沒集結或攻擊。林自言未到場，但同意畫面顯示當時現場沒有人集結；而他到場後，亦見不到有人揮動或發射雷射筆，也沒人攻擊其小隊。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/NFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FNFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y%2F&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUigAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=0f10aa52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FNFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y%2F&h=86f22216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/NFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y/</a>"},{"pid":"c3aa56af7ac56c1509c4f97bedce0dfc58aa1242","tid":2399650,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d921fb476fa2082015350d144d1e872f9c1f5d4","tid":2399650,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:18:27.000Z","msg":"警稱有逾百人集結堵路 片段證警到場前無人集結<br />\n<br />\n林盤問下稱，他於下午3時發現牛頭角道附近有人堵路前，並沒收到通知稱現場有人聚集或有警員受襲。辯方播放現場閉路電視片段，顯示警方到達前兩分鐘，被告與一名女士經過，當時現場並沒集結或攻擊。林自言未到場，但同意畫面顯示當時現場沒有人集結；而他到場後，亦見不到有人揮動或發射雷射筆，也沒人攻擊其小隊。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/NFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FNFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y%2F&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUigAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=0f10aa52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FNFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y%2F&h=86f22216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/NFRJ3R7A5BHGFGML6UTASHPV3Y/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"見到朋友仔咁撚猛"},{"pid":"bc534a909e61fa056cbdceeb65cc0c7545de048b","tid":2399650,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24903854bab1b3d14a17cd116ba05daef4e59a81","tid":2399650,"uid":76674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"個官真係姓屈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021